  {% call example("With Border") %}
<div class="accordion rounded-xl border">
  <details name="accordion-border" class="border-b last:border-b-0 px-4">
    <summary>
      What payment methods do you accept?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, and Apple Pay.</div>
  </details>
  <details name="accordion-border" class="border-b last:border-b-0 px-4">
    <summary>
      Can I cancel my subscription?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>Yes. You can cancel anytime from your account settings. No questions asked.</div>
  </details>
  <details name="accordion-border" class="border-b last:border-b-0 px-4">
    <summary>
      Do you offer refunds?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all plans.</div>
  </details>
</div>
{% endcall %}

  {% call example("In Card") %}
<div class="card max-w-md">
  <header>
    <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <p>Everything you need to know about the product.</p>
  </header>
  <section class="pt-0">
    <div class="accordion">
    <details name="accordion-card" open>
      <summary>
        How does billing work?
        <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </summary>
      <div>Plans are billed monthly or annually. You'll be charged at the start of each billing cycle.</div>
    </details>
    <details name="accordion-card">
      <summary>
        Can I change my plan later?
        <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </summary>
      <div>Yes, you can upgrade or downgrade at any time. Changes take effect on your next billing cycle.</div>
    </details>
    <details name="accordion-card">
      <summary>
        Is there a free trial?
        <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </summary>
      <div>Yes, we offer a 14-day free trial on all paid plans. No credit card required.</div>
    </details>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
{% endcall %}

{% endblock %}
